org.swixml.layoutconverters
Class BorderLayoutConverter

java.lang.Object
  org.swixml.layoutconverters.BorderLayoutConverter
All Implemented Interfaces:
LayoutConverter
public class BorderLayoutConverter
extends Object
implements LayoutConverter

A layout converter for java.awt.BorderLayout.

Examples:

 <panel layout="BorderLayout">
   <panel constraints="BorderLayout.NORTH" />
   <panel constraints="BorderLayout.CENTER" />
 </panel>
 
 <panel layout="BorderLayout(10,20)">
   <panel constraints="NORTH" />
   <panel constraints="CENTER" />
 </panel>
 
 <panel>
   <layout type="BorderLayout" hgap="10" vgap="20"/>
   <panel constraints="NORTH" />
   <panel constraints="CENTER" />
 </panel>

Author:
Karl Tauber, Wolf Paulus
